<p>Klipsam instantly connects people everywhere to what&rsquo;s most  meaningful to them. Any registered user can send a klip, which is a  message that is public by default and can  include other content like photos, videos, and links to other websites.</p>
<p class="tip"><span class="tip">Tip</span> What you say on Klipsam may be viewed all around the world instantly.</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 10px;">This Privacy Policy describes how and when Klipsam collects, uses and  shares your information when you use our Services. Klipsam receives  your information through our various websites, APIs, email  notifications, applications, buttons, widgets, and ads (the "<strong>Services</strong>" or "Klipsam")  and from our partners and other third parties. For example, you send us  information when you use Klipsam from our website, post or receive klips, or access Klipsam from an application such as Klipsam  for Mac, Klipsam for Android or klipDeck. When using any of our  Services you consent to the collection, transfer, manipulation, storage,  disclosure and other uses of your information as described in this  Privacy Policy. Irrespective of which country you reside in or supply  information from, you authorize Klipsam to use your information in any country where Klipsam operates.</p>
<p>If you have any questions or comments about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@Klipsam.com">privacy@Klipsam.com</a> or <a href="/contact">here</a>.</p>
